Apple's <a href="https://www.macrumors.com/roundup/wwdc/">WWDC 2025</a> begins today, with the event kicking off at 10:00 am Pacific Time via the traditional opening keynote. We know that some <em>MacRumors</em> readers who can't follow the event as it's being broadcast are interested in avoiding all of the announcements and waiting until the event video is available for on-demand viewing so as to experience it without already knowing the outcome. <br/>
<br/>
